<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٨٧٢)</span> السؤال: هل يجوزُ للمُسلِم<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>